block-definition.s: predict if kudzu is invasive in %'state name'

block.comment: Choose a feature from the custom tab and the drag it into the "feature name" box. Then drag the state name in the function title into the "state name" box.

This If block is responsible for making prediction with the selected feature value of the given state name passed into this function. This should reflect the decision tree that you created in the first two days.
return true, meaning predict kudzu is invasive in the given state.
return false, meaning predict kudzu is not invasive in the given state.
